, and number of P2P\ncommunication rounds. Our numerical evaluation demonstrates the superiority of\nour proposed scheme over baselines in terms of model training efficiency,\nconvergence rate, system latency, and robustness against model poisoning\nattacks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Mar 2022 00:38:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 03:41:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-05"}
