 of Bragg spots with rotation of the sample about the reflection\nvector. The two principal topics of our studies, polar magnetism and the\nchemical bond in alpha-RuCl3, are brought together in a minimal model of\nmagnetic Ru ions in Cc2/m.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Mar 2022 11:27:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Sep 2022 11:45:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 30 Oct 2022 09:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-01"}
